WHAT IS LAIGUS?

LaiGus is clean and elegant corporate and business Wordpress theme that can be switched as business and portfolio template. There's many page templates available, one slideshow in home page, Portfolio post type, custom shortcodes and more. Please explore demo site or follow features.

---------------------

KEY FEATURES OVERVIEW:

- Neat And Clean Portfolio/Corporate Theme
- Options to enable disable Home page elements
- Home Page Blog and Portfolio Options
- Nivo Slider
- Shortcodes
- Valid XHTML
- 3 Widget Areas
- Custom Post Type
- Full Width Template Page
- 2 Portfolio Template Page
- Contact Us Template Page
- About Template Page
- Home Template Page
- Sitemap Template Page
- Native Contact Form
- jQuery Drop-down menu
- ThimThumb Auto Thumbnail Support
- Support for WordPress custom navigation menus
- Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn and YouTube Integrations
- Compatibility ( IE 7 , IE 8 , Firefox, Opera, Safari, Chrome)